article.description: — EJ Bellinger had 13 points in Tennessee State's 65-55 victory over Lindenwood on Thursday.
article.headline: Bellinger's 13 help Tennessee State knock off Lindenwood 65-55
article.linkText: Bellinger's 13 help Tennessee State knock off Lindenwood 65-55
article.story: SAINT CHARLES, Mo -- — EJ Bellinger had 13 points in Tennessee State's 65-55 victory over Lindenwood on Thursday. Bellinger also had six rebounds for the Tigers (14-10, 7-4 Ohio Valley Conference). Marcus Fitzgerald Jr. scored 12 points while shooting 3 for 6 (3 for 4 from 3-point range) and 3 of 5 from the free throw line. Kinyon Hodges was 3 of 8 shooting and 4 of 5 from the free throw line to finish with 10 points. Keenon Cole led the Lions (8-16, 2-9) in scoring, finishing with 16 points. Darius Beane added 10 points for Lindenwood. In addition, Colin Ruffin had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
